  <div class="container" style="max-width: 1050px;min-height: 600px;"> 
   <div class="row"> 
    <div class="col-md-9"> 
     <div class="row floor-list"> 
      <div class="col-md-12"> 
       <p class="font-14"> </p>
       <p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei';"><strong><span style="font-size: 21px;">牌手故事：你经历过的最诡异的异常状况是什么？</span></strong></span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">楼主：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　这个帖子的目的不是发表一些bad beat的故事，而是发表一些你看到过或经历过的诡异的异常状况。我认为收集一些这样的东西能帮助我们拓展视野。譬如，我注意到上周最诡异的事情是我已经好久没用口袋对子击中过暗三条了。所以，我开始跟踪这种现象。在那周我发到过42个口袋对子，在这些牌局当中（包括翻牌圈、转牌圈和河牌圈）我一次也没有击中过暗三条。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　我觉得这种情况很有意思，也绝对是一种异常状况。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　那么你们经历过的异常状况呢？</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">精彩回复摘选：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Mike09990</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　昨晚在锦标赛上连续错过了13次同花听牌，虽然我每次都没看到河牌。我觉得13是个不幸的数字……</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">DePokerGod</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　拿着AQ和别人单挑。翻牌是A Q Q。对手全压，我跟注，他亮出了JJ。转牌J，河牌J。在翻牌圈我有99.4%的优势拿下底池。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Zeppy</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　我有次在附近的赌场打现场扑克。九名玩家参与的满员桌现金局，荷官在五手牌内给同一名玩家发了三次四条10。那家伙应该跑去买六合彩，看看他逆天的运气能不能持续，但他只是坐在那儿露齿而笑，表现得有点尴尬。</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Efils_god</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">我只见过两次翻牌圈击中四条，而那两次居然是背靠背的，而且是同一个玩家。这算不算异常状况？</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Miamicheats</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　我见过某玩家在他最初十手牌中拿到七次口袋AA，而且他全部获胜，从200美元打到2500美元……</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">MrBump</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　看见Tony G（立陶宛籍著名牌手，以松凶著称）在翻前弃过一次牌。太诡异了。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Kimes</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　我朋友（女孩）只对手牌大小有一点点了解，但她连续赢了三次家庭sng牌局。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Salats</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　翻前用AA和两个reg玩家的KK打到全压。这辈子赢得最轻松的两个买入。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">楼主：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　打2/5级别的扑克，一个激进的鱼玩家每次在UTG位置都要straddle（发牌之前预先加注）。但他每次straddle的运气都非常好，连续四次不是AA就是KＫ。每次他straddle加注就有一两名玩家等着全压对抗他，认为他在“偷盲”。于是这条鱼在一个半小时内赢了四千美元。羡慕死我了。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Vektor</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　我曾经在PLO牌局用Q高赢了一个三人全压的对局。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Lana_Lang</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　开多桌，在全部四张桌子同时拿到AA，做了切幕保存。我清楚地记得我当时的想法是“哈哈哈，如果我在这四张桌子都翻前全压，我应该可以得到至少一个跟注。”然后，我确实做到了，我得到了两个跟注，一张桌子一个跟注，都输了……　</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Craps_shooter</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　打了三十万手牌，从未拿到过皇家同花顺。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Hoverroundon22s</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　有次连续两次发到口袋AA，翻前全压，两局都赢了。还有一次手气好到爆，在扑克之星25手牌内发到22手Hellmuths所说的“最好的五副起手牌”。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">PayOffWizard1987</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　我在实体赌场曾经有一次连续六把发到AK。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Rip_AA</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　一天内拿到两次皇家同花顺。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　在nl100打现金局，一晚上赢了30多个买入。难忘的2007年啊……</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Nathan Zamora</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　18岁那年，</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 19px;">我</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 19px;">在一家地下扑克室连续五次发到AA。当时觉得某人想把我宰了……</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">Ech0s</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: '微软雅黑','sans-serif'">：</span></strong></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">　　我连续打了八年扑克，在那段时间只拿到过两次四条。上个月的一周，我拿到了12次四条。有一天两次在翻牌圈就击中了四条，还有一天拿到了三次四条。</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">原帖链接：</span></strong></p>
       <p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'"><a href="http://forumserver.twoplustwo.com/54/poker-beats-brags-variance/weirdest-poker-anamolies-variance-youve-experienced-1160906/index.html">http://forumserver.twoplustwo.com/54/poker-beats-brags-variance/weirdest-poker-anamolies-variance-youve-experienced-1160906/index.html</a></span></p>
       <p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif'">&nbsp;</span></p>
